<br>
The problem is that planar mobs below 30% health will regen to 30% if the highest person on the hate list gets too far away from them. <br>
<br>
There's a few solutions, one that is to mez your ex pet and charm another to kill him.<br>
<br>
Another is to break charm only when your pet is in run mode, better controlled by slowing the mobs you kill.<br>
<br>
Or to rune yourself, break charm, root it, slow it so it's not too dangerous on root break, making it easier to stay closer and avoid the regen problem, and then nuke it into run mode<br>
